  "description": "A stunning nighttime long-exposure photograph captures a vibrant fireworks display over a city skyline and multiple bridges. A large, spherical firework bursts in the upper center, radiating brilliant white and reddish-orange light. Below the firework, the city\u2019s buildings are illuminated with golden and white lights, creating a dazzling urban landscape. Two prominent bridges stretch across the dark water; one is a classic suspension bridge with visible towers and cables, and the other a modern, sleek cable-stayed bridge. The water reflects some of the city lights and fireworks. The foreground is mostly dark, emphasizing the brightness of the illuminated cityscape and the fireworks.",
